      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARGYLE EMMA (2) latest effort finished 4th on May 15 over 300m at Healesville behind Jaded Smile beaten 5.5 lengths (17.06) in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and rates on top. MISS LADY BUG (5) was safely held in tougher company last start after drifting back at Ballarat, but prior to that won easily by 3.5 lengths at Ballarat (22.50) beating Key Begonia in a Grade 5 on May 4. Should be thereabouts. PUNCH DRUNK LOVE (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Ballarat behind Motivate (26.14) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. MORAINE MIA (1) has been freshened and can sneak into the frame on her best form.",
